import re

def solve(url):
    match = re.search(r'\d{4}\/\d{2}\/\d{2}', url)
    if match:
        date_str = match.group()
        year = date_str[:4]
        month = date_str[5:7]
        day = date_str[8:]
        return year, month, day
    else:
        return None
